&lt;h2 id="a-question-before-booking"&gt;A question before booking?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to chat first or find out more before making an appointment,
write to me at &lt;a href="mailto:contact@enso-psychologie.ch"&gt;contact@enso-psychologie.ch&lt;/a&gt;
— I will get back to you as soon as possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Contact</title><link>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/contact/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/contact/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Legal notice</title><link>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/legal/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/legal/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="site-owner"&gt;Site owner&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guillaume Bassand
FSP AVP Psychologist
Lausanne, Vaud, Switzerland
&lt;a href="mailto:contact@enso-psychologie.ch"&gt;contact@enso-psychologie.ch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="professional-title"&gt;Professional title&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The title of psychologist is protected in Switzerland under the Federal Act on
Psychology Professions (PsyG) of 18 March 2011. Guillaume Bassand holds a Master&amp;rsquo;s
degree in Psychology recognised by the Swiss Confederation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="member-of"&gt;Member of&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swiss Federation of Psychologists (FSP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vaud Association of Psychologists (AVP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="hosting"&gt;Hosting&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This website is hosted by GitHub Pages (GitHub, Inc., San Francisco, CA, USA).
For more information on data processing by GitHub:
&lt;a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"&gt;https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Privacy policy</title><link>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/privacy/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://enso-psychologie.ch/en/privacy/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="data-controller"&gt;Data controller&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Guillaume Bassand — &lt;a href="mailto:contact@enso-psychologie.ch"&gt;contact@enso-psychologie.ch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="data-collected"&gt;Data collected&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This website does not actively collect any personal data. No forms, tracking cookies
or third-party analytics tools are used.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The only data processed are standard access logs automatically collected by the hosting
provider GitHub Pages (IP address, browser, pages visited, date and time). These are
managed by GitHub Inc. in accordance with their own
&lt;a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"&gt;privacy policy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="contact-by-email"&gt;Contact by email&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you write to &lt;a href="mailto:contact@enso-psychologie.ch"&gt;contact@enso-psychologie.ch&lt;/a&gt;, your data (name, email address, message
content) are used solely to respond to your enquiry. They are not shared with third
parties and are not subject to any automated processing.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>